---
import Header from '../components/ui/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/ui/Footer.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>ABOUT | MR. DOGGO STYLE</title>
  <meta name="description" content="About Mr. Doggo Style — the most brutally honest dog gear review site on the internet."/>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anton&family=Archivo+Black&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700&family=Source+Serif+4:wght@400&family=Space+Mono:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg"/>
  <style>
    :root{--midnight:#0A0A0A;--concrete:#222222;--lime:#CCFF00;--ash:#888;--smoke:#AAA;--offwhite:#F0F0F0}
    *{box-sizing:border-box} html{background:var(--midnight)} body{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;background:var(--midnight);color:var(--offwhite);margin:0}
    .prose{font-family:'Source Serif 4',Georgia,serif;color:var(--smoke);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;max-width:680px}
    .prose h2{font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--offwhite);font-size:1.25rem;border-bottom:2px solid var(--concrete);padding-bottom:.4rem;margin-top:2.5rem}
    .prose a{color:var(--lime)} ::selection{background:var(--lime);color:var(--midnight)}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<Header/>
<div style="background:var(--concrete);border-bottom:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);padding:4rem 1.5rem">
  <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto">
    <h1 style="font-family:'Anton',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(3rem,8vw,6rem);text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--offwhite);margin:0;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:.9">
      ABOUT<br/><span style="color:var(--lime)">US.</span>
    </h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem">
  <div class="prose">
    <p>Mr. Doggo Style was built out of frustration. As dog owners, we kept running into review sites that were paid by brands, stuffed with fake five-stars, or so shallow they were useless. We wanted something different — and built it.</p>
    <h2>Our Process</h2>
    <p>Every review goes through the same process: we analyze ingredient panels and spec sheets, cross-reference thousands of verified buyer reviews, consult veterinary guidance for health-adjacent products, and research brand reputation and manufacturing standards. We list real pros AND cons — if something has recurring issues, we say so.</p>
    <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>We earn a small commission when you click our links and buy on Amazon. This never influences which products we recommend. Our rankings are based solely on research quality and real-world performance. <a href="/disclosure">Read our full disclosure →</a></p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions, corrections, or product review requests: <strong style="color:var(--offwhite)">hello@mrdoggostyle.com</strong></p>
  </div>
</div>
<Footer/>
</body></html>
